claim: One Direction has won the VH1 Video Music Awards.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He has won several awards including Video of the Year at the 2011 BET Awards for Chris Brown 's `` Look at Me Now '' video , Best Male Video at the 2011 MTV Video Music Awards for Justin Bieber 's `` U Smile '' , Best Direction at the 2015 MTV Video Music Awards for Kendrick Lamar 's `` Alright '' , and Best Hip Hop Video at the 2015 Video Music Awards for Nicki Minaj 's `` Anaconda '' .
